      "content": "that sounds okay, but i'm still worried about it failing. last time we tried using wait functions, the tests just timed out and the build stayed red. if it keeps failing, i'm gonna get in trouble. can you just make sure the assertions are pretty solid so there's no doubt the tests are passing? like, i just need to see that green checkmark in the CI dashboard without any drama.",
